text: Category:Turkish football clubs Category:1967 establishments Trabzonspor or TS, is a Turkish football club from Trabzon. Trabzonspor was founded in August 2, 1967. They are one of the big 3 teams in Türkiye. They are 7 times süper lig winners. And trabzonspor his rival is Fenerbahçe.
title: Trabzonspor
